// The demo mod bundle. A mod is the SAME shape as the base game: a folder with a
// `*.bundle.ron` manifest listing its content files (paths relative to this
// folder). This one has a single content file that both OVERRIDES a base section
// and ADDS a new scenario. It is listed in `assets/mods.catalog.ron`; enable it from
// the main-menu Mods section (or by adding its id to `EnabledMods`).
(content: ["mod.content.ron"])
